-- Tabreed Is Awarding Contracts for Eight Plants That Will Serve Dubai Metro
-- B y   I n a l   E r s a n
-- 2010-11-09T07:14:32Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-09/tabreed-is-awarding-contracts-for-eight-plants-that-will-serve-dubai-metro.html
National Central Cooling Co., known
as Tabreed, said it is in the process of awarding contracts for
eight new plants that would serve a Dubai Metro line.  The company said it built five new plants and expanded two
others in the third quarter and has three plants and two
expansions under construction, according to a statement to the
Dubai bourse today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Inal Ersan at 
 iersan@bloomberg.net  